title: dj yoda - how to cut & paste, 80's edition
description:
clever hip hop mix from yoda including a diverse range of samples from classic 80\&#039;s films (ferris beuller\&#039;s day off and the goonies) t.v shows (Dallas, Knight Rider) computer games and commercials, as well as some great 80\&#039;s rap and hip hop tracks. Great for when you\&#039;re feeling nostalgic...made me laugh out loud.

enjoy xxx
